HOWTO

Test this project by simply run the following command in PWD. 
./run.sh

NOTICE: 
After deleting the output directories, you will be led into the pig Grunt command line, 
within the command line, you can run the program by typing "run proj3.pig". 

Concerning the layout of the files and directories, I recommend to change
to my user name w234sxg with passwd w234sxg

